data.name: BookEdited_HelpText
data.value:
A single or multi-volume work with discrete contributions from various authors which is compiled by one or more editors. Includes dictionaries and encyclopedias.

An edited book which does not have a publisher should added with the Report or Gray Literature reference type.

data.name: Book_HelpText
data.value: A single independent, complete work, written by one author or a team of authors who share the responsibility of the text (in one volume or a finite set of volumes).

data.value:

To cite a single work from a collected work, use the Contribution reference type.
